06:23.724 --> 06:25.470
- Fucking hell.

06:25.470 --> 06:26.303
Right, room 16.

06:26.303 --> 06:27.600
Let's go.
- [Liza] Yes, sir.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.100
This is your Caribbean building.

06:29.100 --> 06:30.560
- The Caribbean?

06:30.560 --> 06:31.940
- Caribbean, Caribbean, yes.

06:31.940 --> 06:35.410
- And what part of this
resembles the Caribbean?

06:35.410 --> 06:37.800
- [Liza] I think it's more
so because of the view.

06:37.800 --> 06:38.830
- [Gordon] Oh, the view.

06:38.830 --> 06:40.190
