- [Gordon] What is this?

14:58.460 --> 14:59.970
Wow.

14:59.970 --> 15:00.873
Oh, man.

15:02.250 --> 15:03.260
Look at them.

15:03.260 --> 15:04.743
The water's gone slimy.

