15:22.330 --> 15:24.300
- Why it's like that, I have no idea.

15:24.300 --> 15:26.800
- [Gordon] It's festered,
it's off, it's bubbling.

15:29.960 --> 15:31.730
Oh, man.

15:31.730 --> 15:33.000
- That's terrible.
- Fuck.

15:33.000 --> 15:34.753
- Trash, please, trash.

15:35.920 --> 15:37.470
James, trash please, now.

15:37.470 --> 15:40.220
- Pina colada.
- Right down the drain.

15:40.220 --> 15:43.223
- [Gordon] By the bucket
load in the walk-in fridge.

15:46.950 --> 15:50.340
I mean, who in the hell
operates like this?

15:50.340 --> 15:52.300
- Gordon, this is Chef Ben's job.

15:52.300 --> 15:53.470
He's the executive chef.

15:53.470 --> 15:54.800
- [Gordon] The executive chef.

15:54.800 --> 15:56.680
And you've made him that
executive chef, right?

15:56.680 --> 15:57.877
- Sure I did.

15:57.877 --> 15:59.427
- [Gordon] How do you feel now?

16:01.250 --> 16:02.650
What's that?
- [Brian] Tuna burger.

16:02.650 --> 16:03.860
- [Gordon] That's from the burger?

16:03.860 --> 16:04.693
- [Brian] Yes, it is.

16:04.693 --> 16:06.850
- [Gordon] Oh, my God, seriously?

16:06.850 --> 16:07.683
- [Brian] Bacon.

16:07.683 --> 16:09.350
- [Gordon] It's gone, and it's off.

16:09.350 --> 16:12.230
Fresh produce on top
