16:12.230 --> 16:13.260
And this one?

16:13.260 --> 16:14.093
- [Brian] Rib eye.

16:14.093 --> 16:15.820
- [Gordon] Rib eye defrosting.

16:15.820 --> 16:17.060
What is this?

16:17.060 --> 16:18.660
- [Brian] Those are the
smoked grilled chicken wings

16:18.660 --> 16:20.830
