16:20.830 --> 16:23.533
- [Gordon] Oh, my God,
and what is in this one?

16:24.700 --> 16:25.823
You are kidding me.

16:26.770 --> 16:29.370
So underneath in that bucket's what?

16:29.370 --> 16:31.940
- [Brian] Cooked product.
- [Gordon] Cooked chicken.

16:31.940 --> 16:34.860
