- It's raw.

16:34.860 --> 16:37.470
- Raw chicken on top of cooked chicken.

16:37.470 --> 16:38.763
I had them for lunch.

16:39.660 --> 16:42.200
I am at a fucking loss.

16:42.200 --> 16:43.830
Do you know the best way out of this

16:43.830 --> 16:45.380
is just to shut the place down.

16:46.725 --> 16:48.173
- That's not an option for me.

16:49.890 --> 16:50.980
- What's that in there, Ben?

16:50.980 --> 16:52.260
- Those are marinated chicken wings.

16:52.260 --> 16:53.540
- [Gordon] Yeah.
- [Ben] To be smoked.

16:53.540 --> 16:55.223
- [Gordon] Underneath, next box.

16:56.270 --> 16:58.060
- [Ben] Those are smoked.

16:58.060 --> 17:01.940
- Rule number fucking one, Ben.

17:01.940 --> 17:03.663
- I know, Chef, I didn't do it.

17:04.753 --> 17:05.849
You know, I turn my back for a minute,

17:05.849 --> 17:07.310
