17:07.310 --> 17:09.492
- I walked in, and it was bedlam.

17:11.118 --> 17:12.240
- Mm-hmm, mm-hmm.

17:12.240 --> 17:13.740
- He's telling me this is your fault.

17:13.740 --> 17:14.780
You've got no idea.

17:14.780 --> 17:17.323
I am at an absolute fucking loss.

17:18.380 --> 17:20.369
I can't work like this.

17:20.369 --> 17:22.550
This is huge.

17:22.550 --> 17:27.223
You now are running a
restaurant cross-contaminated.

17:30.914 --> 17:33.914
(suspenseful music)

17:35.040 --> 17:36.340
Joey?
- [Joey] Yes, Chef?

17:36.340 --> 17:37.790
- Who's responsible for this?

17:38.920 --> 17:41.290
- We all are, the entire kitchen is, Chef.

17:41.290 --> 17:42.710
- Rule number one,

17:42.710 --> 17:45.050
you can't put hot food
in a fucking walk-in.

17:45.050 --> 17:46.730
It doesn't even go together.

17:46.730 --> 17:47.610
- No, not at all.

17:47.610 --> 17:48.980
Nowhere near each other.

17:48.980 --> 17:50.670
