a fucking massive disaster.

18:02.320 --> 18:04.810
- I mean, who the hell put
them on top of the other ones?

18:04.810 --> 18:05.643
Everybody in here knows better.

18:05.643 --> 18:06.476
- Brian, if I knew--

18:06.476 --> 18:07.526
- [Brian] Haven't you trained
everybody to know that?

18:07.526 --> 18:08.827
- Yeah.
- I mean...

18:08.827 --> 18:11.420
- [Gordon] All I'm getting
right now is excuses.

18:11.420 --> 18:13.590
The kitchen needs direction from the chef.

18:13.590 --> 18:16.970
The staff need direction from
the owner, and you're buddies.

18:16.970 --> 18:19.170
Can someone come up
with a fucking solution?

18:20.940 --> 18:22.530
- I'm gonna go and 86 the wings.

18:22.530 --> 18:26.163
- Sort it out quickly.
- Come on, guys.

18:27.110 --> 18:28.580
- [James] 86 wings.

18:28.580 --> 18:29.980
- [Ben] Someone put raw
fucking chicken wings

18:29.980 --> 18:31.110
