18:31.110 --> 18:33.820
It wasn't me, somebody else did it.

18:33.820 --> 18:35.620
86 wings is the only
thing I can do right now.

18:35.620 --> 18:37.570
- [Gordon] What in the fuck is going on?

18:37.570 --> 18:39.090
- [James] I was baffled and amazed.

18:39.090 --> 18:40.417
The words out of Ben's mouth were,

18:40.417 --> 18:42.717
