back in when he wants.

19:09.110 --> 19:10.870
- Pretty much, pretty much, yeah.

19:10.870 --> 19:12.570
- But if this was your business,
you wouldn't tolerate that.

19:12.570 --> 19:14.073
- No, I would have fired
Ben a long time ago.

19:14.073 --> 19:16.820
I was all for firing Ben
two months ago, so I mean...

19:19.240 --> 19:22.330
- [Brian] No excuse for that
walk-in like that, so...

