- I'm sorry, I just
couldn't hold back anymore.

19:24.160 --> 19:25.680
He doesn't come to work.

19:25.680 --> 19:27.290
That's the reason why it
looks like that, okay?

19:27.290 --> 19:29.700
That's absolutely the reason why.

